    <briefdescription>
<para>Call an arbitrary function with the raw value from a ControlPacket. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Escape hatch for non-standard output logic — e.g. a value that maps to motor positions, PWM brightness, or multi-bit state machines that do not fit the <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1LED" kindref="compound">LED</ref> pattern. Mirrors DcsBios::IntegerBuffer.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keywordtype">void</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>onCanopyPos(uint16_t<sp/>v)<sp/>{<sp/>analogWrite(CANOPY_MOTOR,<sp/>v<sp/>&gt;&gt;<sp/>8);<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1IntegerOutput" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk::IntegerOutput</ref><sp/>canopy(<ref refid="A4EC__OutputIds_8h_1a35e95f5bc2473cf12af79fa81984ee4f" kindref="member">A_4E_C_CANOPY_POS</ref>,<sp/>onCanopyPos);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
